sentences.english: Monthly maintenance doses can be administered in either the deltoid or gluteal muscle.
sentences.chinese: 每月維持劑量可以注射在三角肌或臀肌。

sentences.english: The deltoid muscle is small in infants and young children.
sentences.chinese: 嬰兒和幼兒的三角肌很小。

sentences.english: The upper trapezius in the back and the anterior deltoids at the front of the shoulders lift the arms.
sentences.chinese: 背部的上斜方肌和肩膀前側的前三角肌上提手臂。

sentences.english: Gradually he felt his deltoids becoming sore.
sentences.chinese: 漸漸他覺得兩臂上的三角肌發酸。

sentences.english: The middle portions of the deltoids abduct the shoulders, drawing them away from the trunk.
sentences.chinese: 三角肌中部使肩膀外展，將肩膀向遠離軀幹的方向拉。
